&nbsp;
The investigation, culminated in the operation "Saracena", conducted by the military of the Operational Nucleus of the Company of Randazzo and coordinated by the Dda of Catania, shed light on the activities of the thigh linked to the family of the Mazzei, identifying the elements of summit active in Bronte, Maniace, Maletto and in the surrounding areas.
&nbsp;
