&nbsp;
The elements collected allowed the prosecutor to request and obtain from the gip of Catania the precaution against 18 inquired, while for a further investigation the measure will be evaluated after the preventive interrogation. 15 further investigations will be notified of the notice of conclusion of preliminary investigations. &nbsp;
